The paper focuses on image captioning, which is a task in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of neural networks (cs.NE) and natural language processing (cs.CL) in the image captioning system. The analysis of the image representation and its impact on the performance of the system suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper discusses the clustering of images based on visual and linguistic information, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM).
